_:Nda215ed0798f45d5b4b1cbd1d17510b4 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Baroness Anderson of Stoke-on-Trent was appointed Baroness in Waiting (Government Whip) on 11 July 2024. She was appointed as Parliamentary Secretary in the Cabinet Office on 3 March 2026.</p>\n" .
